Kau hampir terluka.

237
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:08,380
Kau mendengarkan, 'kan?

238
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:11,590
Jangan bermain-main lagi di sini.

239
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:16,980
Lee Han Jo-ssi,

